Association for Relations Across the Taiwan Straits, met here
today with William Cohen, defense secretary of the United States,
and the two sides held talks on the Taiwan issue.
</P>
<P>
Wang said that the U.S. government should honor its commitments,
and the differences across the straits will be resolved in line
with the One-China principle, adding these are of significance for
the security of the Asian-Pacific region, the development of Sino-
U.S. relations and world peace.
</P>
<P>
