deeds, and hopes to discuss reunification and cooperation with the
Taiwan authorities on the premise of the One-China principle, he
added.
</P>
<P>
Cohen said that the U.S. government will observe the One-China
principle, and the U.S. values its relations with China, and will
make improvement in this regard.
