here today with William Cohen, defense secretary of the United
States.
</P>
<P>
Xu said that in 1972, the late U.S. President Richard Nixon and
Chinese late Premier Zhou Enlai signed the well-known Sino-U.S.
Shanghai Joint Communique just in the hall where they are meeting.
