- - - -
</P>
<P>
NEW DELHI -- Exports of Information Technology (IT) industry,
software services and electronics grew at an impressive 36 percent
to reach 5.46 billion U.S. dollars in 1999-2000, an official
statement released by the Ministry of Commerce said Thursday.
</P>
<P>
