<P>
Pop music soirees will be held at the odeum every Friday
evening. New songs as well as new singers will be introduced to
the audience while classic pop songs will be reviewed.
</P>
<P>
The completion of the odeum indicates that the status of pop
music as an art has been further confirmed in the country, experts
said.
</P>
<P>
Before the odeum's construction, China had not a single odeum
that was dedicated to pop music shows, despite of the fact that
pop music has won a multitude of fans nationwide.
</P>
<P>
Pop singers usually performed in discos and karaoke clubs, with
some top-rated ones occasionally singing at TV shows.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
